HEADWORD: Deposer
<hw>De*pos"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who
deposes or degrades from office.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One who testifies or deposes; a deponent.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Deposit</ent>⟦br⟧
